From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: cam_system <local>
Date: Wed, 3 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] libjpeg-turbo: remove install rpath

Yocto QA reports /usr/lib install RPATH as useless-rpaths.  The
PetaLinux 2022.2 core libjpeg-turbo recipe carries the same oe-specific
fix for the older 2.1.1 recipe; keep the behavior for the local 3.1.4
recipe instead of disabling QA.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [oe-specific]
---
 CMakeLists.txt | 4 ----
 1 file changed, 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/CMakeLists.txt b/CMakeLists.txt
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -306,10 +306,6 @@ endif()
 report_option(ENABLE_SHARED "Shared libraries")
 report_option(ENABLE_STATIC "Static libraries")
 
-if(ENABLE_SHARED)
-  set(CMAKE_INSTALL_RPATH ${CMAKE_INSTALL_FULL_LIBDIR})
-endif()
-
 if(WITH_JPEG8 OR WITH_JPEG7)
   set(WITH_ARITH_ENC 1)
   set(WITH_ARITH_DEC 1)
-- 
2.37.2
